data.description: This home is in the desirable Turkey Creek community. This charming residence offers a comfortable and relaxed lifestyle. With its 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, wood-burning fireplace, and an expansive backyard, this property is perfect for those seeking a warm and inviting place to call their own. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed floor plan that maximizes space and functionality. Gather around the cozy wood-burning fireplace, adding warmth and ambiance to the living room. The well-appointed newly painted kitchen has been updated with granite countertops, new tile flooring, and features beautiful hardwood oak cabinets, offering ample storage space for all your culinary needs. The large Master Bedroom includes a walk-in closet, full bath with dual sinks, walk in shower, and jetted tub. Several rooms have been freshly painted. The guest rooms are spacious along with the full guest bath that has been updated with new tile floors. The backyard is perfect for outdoor activities and entertainment. This home also offers a side entry oversized two car garage. The oversized lot offers plenty of space for gardening, playing, and hosting gatherings. As a resident of the Turkey Creek community, you'll have access to a wide range of amenities, including tennis courts, pickleball courts, a sparkling pool, golf course, and restaurant. Enjoy an active and vibrant lifestyle right at your doorstep. Located close to shopping, dining and minutes from the interstate, recreational and medical facilities. Make this home yours today!
